schema_description: Table contains high level OSR zones data: how many open positions and totes exists in particular OSR zone at a given timestamp.

fields.description: The time when current values of capacity were received.
fields.name: created

fields.description: Number of positions in the zone occupied by empty totes.
fields.name: empty_positions

fields.description: Number of positions in the zone not occupied by totes.
fields.name: free_positions

fields.description: Maximum number of totes the zone can contain for given MFC.
fields.name: total_positions

fields.description: Name of zone inside OSR. Possible values: raw, refrigerated, ambient.
fields.name: zone_name
